# Docker ignore file for clinical-diary development environments
# Excludes unnecessary files from Docker build context

# Version control
**/.git
**/.github
**/.gitignore

# Dependencies
**/node_modules
**/pub-cache
**/.pub-cache
**/flutter/.pub-cache

# Build outputs
**/build
**/dist
**/out
**/.dart_tool
**/coverage
**/*.lcov

# IDE
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs

# Temporary files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/.temp

# Environment files (may contain secrets)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Test artifacts
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Documentation (not needed in build)
**/docs
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md

# Untracked notes (working documents)
**/untracked-notes

# Archive
**/archive

# Evaluation materials
**/evaluation

# Linear CLI tools (not needed in containers)
**/tools/linear-cli

# Requirement validation tools (not needed in containers)
**/tools/requirements
